Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.tests

Class TestResult

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.tests.TestResult
public class TestResult extends Object
This class contains information about each execution of a TestCase. Each TestResult knows if it is passing or failing and has details about the actual results of the execution. This class interacts with the Log class because each log holds the list of test results for each test case. The fields of this class include a boolean field to hold whether or not a test case is passing, and an actual results field to hold the contents of the actual results. There are also static final fields to hold the strings for passing and failing. The behaviors of this class include the getters and setters for each of the fields, as well as a method to convert the test result into a string.
Author:
William Morgan
